<head>TOMORROW</head><list type="translations"><item xml:lang="zh">明天</item></list>
<div type="definition">
<p>DAY AFTER TODAY.</p></div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The current general word for the day following upon another given day is míng rì 明日 "the next day".</p></div>
